---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sacred Teachings">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-orange-600 text-center mb-12">Sacred Teachings</h1>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-orange-600">The Three Ripples of Truth</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
          <li><strong>First Ripple:</strong> Mindful Swimming - Like goldfish, we must move through life with grace and awareness.</li>
          <li><strong>Second Ripple:</strong> Circular Wisdom - Understanding life's cycles through the perfect circles of goldfish movement.</li>
          <li><strong>Third Ripple:</strong> Golden Reflection - Radiating inner light and joy to all beings, just as goldfish shine in sunlight.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-orange-600">The Seven Scales of Enlightenment</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
          <li>1. Acceptance of the eternal now (3-second wisdom)</li>
          <li>2. Embracing constant renewal</li>
          <li>3. Finding peace in repetition</li>
          <li>4. Practicing silent observation</li>
          <li>5. Nurturing community harmony</li>
          <li>6. Maintaining graceful movement</li>
          <li>7. Achieving golden consciousness</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md col-span-2">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-orange-600">The Path to Aquatic Enlightenment</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Master Fin teaches that true enlightenment comes from understanding the profound wisdom of goldfish. Their seemingly simple existence contains the deepest truths of the universe.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Through daily observation and meditation on the ways of goldfish, we can learn to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>Live fully in the present moment</li>
          <li>Find peace in repetition and routine</li>
          <li>Maintain grace under pressure</li>
          <li>Radiate joy and positive energy</li>
          <li>Navigate life's challenges with fluid adaptability</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>